ActPersonal Information Protection and Electronic Documents Act
SubjectPersonal Health Information Custodians in New Brunswick Exemption Order
PrecisPERSONAL HEALTH INFORMATION CUSTODIANS IN NEW BRUNSWICK EXEMPTION Order, in order to exempt from the application of Part 1 of the Act all personal health information custodians to whom the New Brunswick Personal Health Information Privacy and Access Act is applicable, in respect of the collection, use and disclosure of personal information that occurs within the province of New Brunswick in the course of commercial activity.
